{"tid":2026412,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旺角男子通宵兩晚打麻將　車上大睡惹昏迷虛驚","createTime":"2020-05-21T02:42:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T02:52:06.000Z","uid":6497,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"756404d61b8091d4cc05836d5de75681e773d19d","tid":2026412,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T02:42:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200521/s00001/1590025713598/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200521%2Fs00001%2F1590025713598%2F&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=0dbbf2a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200521%2Fs00001%2F1590025713598%2F&h=da7d39f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200521/s00001/1590025713598/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200521/s00001/11ac8b28ec03c4953246d16fba0f8600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200521%2Fs00001%2F11ac8b28ec03c4953246d16fba0f8600.jpg&h=8335572c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昨晚（20日）11時49分，有司機駛經旺角洗衣街39號金雞廣場對開時，發現一輛七人車違泊路邊，司機在車上疑昏迷，擔心有人倒斃車上，於是報警求助。消防到場破開副駕駛座車窗，其間事主回復清醒，經救護員檢查後確認身體無恙。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指出，男事主報稱連打兩晚通宵麻將致精神迷糊，遂於車上休息，引起誤會。事後事主自行乘車離開，其友人到場駕走七人車。"},{"pid":"a3d51b1d793bee2ca2a507659109b0efd6e11f8c","tid":2026412,"uid":157901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T02:43:59.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18cfcca8b04796755d1386e591999a185d3375cb","tid":2026412,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T02:50:02.000Z","msg":"仲報狗<img src=\"/asset